Package com.thoughtworks.go.plugin.api.material.packagerepository

Interface Summary
PackageMaterialConfiguration PackageMaterialConfiguration encapsulates all the methods which will be used to capture the configurations related to the package and the repository.
PackageMaterialPoller PackageMaterialPoller encapsulates all methods which are required to communicate with package repository.
PackageMaterialProvider PackageMaterialProvider class is the staring point for package repository as material plugin.
